00:34:34,721 --> 00:34:38,925
you kind of think about the game you'd make if you had infinite money and a massive team and if you were, you know...

713
00:34:40,017 --> 00:34:42,360
the perfect overlord of a

714
00:34:42,860 --> 00:34:43,762
of infinite resources

