00:39:02,171 --> 00:39:05,794
one day and then when you're like when you're halfway down that list and you've

803
00:39:05,814 --> 00:39:09,478
done the most important half of those things it's really easy to cut the rest

804
00:39:09,498 --> 00:39:14,343
because it's been three fucking years just like I just need to fucking release this

805
00:39:16,510 --> 00:39:18,352
So that's what I did with Gunpoint. Gunpoint, you know, there's...

806
00:39:19,153 --> 00:39:21,715
The to-do list for that is twice as long as the things I actually did.

