00:43:58,043 --> 00:44:01,566
the part time for the level should really be an accurate reflection of my own personal abilities

898
00:44:02,006 --> 00:44:05,549
was actually not the biggest thing I needed fixing, the biggest thing I needed fixing was the game

899
00:44:09,271 --> 00:44:10,692
and the sixth thing I learned was

