00:44:29,720 --> 00:44:31,922
and I had loads and loads of ideas I wanted to put in

906
00:44:32,243 --> 00:44:34,365
and then when I got to the weekend I would have a specific idea of

907
00:44:34,785 --> 00:44:38,369
I want to get this feature in this weekend, I want to get elevators working, I want to do this.

