00:44:43,512 --> 00:44:48,195
and sometimes I would just be not even close, like not even ten percent of the way to getting that thing done

910
00:44:48,615 --> 00:44:52,377
and it would just be soul crushing, I would just feel terrible

911
00:44:52,537 --> 00:44:55,119
and I just felt like an idiot, I just felt like this is, like

