00:44:55,139 --> 00:44:56,579
I was supposed to get this done this weekend

913
00:44:57,040 --> 00:44:59,941
and I'm not going to get it done next weekend or the weekend after

914
00:44:59,961 --> 00:45:03,383
and that's even more crushing when you're working part-time because that's not

