00:45:39,692 --> 00:45:40,953
My reaction to that would not be,

925
00:45:41,033 --> 00:45:42,813
you fucking idiot, what's wrong with you?

926
00:45:42,833 --> 00:45:45,254
It would obviously be, oh, that's interesting.

927
00:45:46,394 --> 00:45:47,294
Thanks for looking into it.

928
00:45:47,834 --> 00:45:48,874
That's valuable data.

929
00:45:49,014 --> 00:45:50,575
We didn't have that information beforehand.

930
00:45:50,675 --> 00:45:51,695
I didn't have it, you didn't have it.

931
00:45:52,015 --> 00:45:53,595
We didn't know how big this job was,

932
00:45:54,035 --> 00:45:55,396
and you have done the valuable work

