00:45:55,436 --> 00:45:57,336
of going out and finding out how big that job was

934
00:45:57,396 --> 00:45:58,056
by trying to do it.

935
00:45:58,436 --> 00:45:59,436
And now we have more information,

936
00:45:59,476 --> 00:46:00,437
we can make better decisions.

