1057
00:51:35,861 --> 00:51:39,087
So it was if I started working too hard

1058
00:51:39,107 --> 00:51:40,230
and then came up with that.

1059
00:51:40,600 --> 00:51:44,623
that schedule to counteract that, and whether I ever did experience burnout.

